{"tid":486690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人仔詐騙錄音","createTime":"2017-12-02T05:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T05:37:36.000Z","uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a89521e60b0f89a96bd3b2350d5bc17f85744f2","tid":486690,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"順豐、入境處已經out 依家出現人仔詐騙錄音<br />\n前幾日收到人仔send黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/133707_0dc502132c093f7999a1311c18dadd4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F133707_0dc502132c093f7999a1311c18dadd4f.jpg&h=61dc88f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知今日真係中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係香港電話號碼打黎<br />\n又係個把女聲話：「你好，你的中國移動流動帳戶出現異常情況，現在按1字為你轉播。」<br />\n咁我㩒1字睇下佢有咩花臣<br />\n點知佢話：「廣東話服務已滿，現為你轉駁普通話服務。」<br />\n咁都得架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉駁之後：<br />\n佢：你好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂<br />\n佢：你的電話數據滿了，歡迎致電服務部。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：Hello？<br />\n佢：你會說普通話嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：Excuse me?<br />\n佢：這裡是普通話服務部，請你說普通話。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：What can I help you？<br />\n佢：我知道你𢤦英文，不要在這裡炫耀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：Can u speak English ?<br />\n**突然轉播音樂**<br />\n佢：Er...What do u from ?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：Let me know who are u first <br />\n佢：去你的八七@%*~#%^ (我聽唔到佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n不過，真係要小心身邊老一輩既人被人呃<br />\n提一提佢地會好d"}]}